VI worry \u2014 I worry that this excitement about colonizing Mars and other planets
p70
aVcarries with it a long, dark shadow:
p71
aVthe implication and belief by some
p72
aVthat Mars will be there to save us from the self-inflicted destruction
p73
aVof the only truly habitable planet we know of, the Earth.
p74
aVAs much as I love interplanetary exploration,
p75
aVI deeply disagree with this idea.
p76
aVThere are many excellent reasons to go to Mars,
p77
aVbut for anyone to tell you that Mars will be there to back up humanity
p78
